sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Controller as ClasseRestController
    participant Service as ClasseServiceImpl
    participant Repo as ClasseRepository
    participant DB as MySQL

    Client->>Controller: POST /api/classes (JSON)
    Controller->>Service: ajouterClasse(classe)
    Service->>Repo: save(classe)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT INTO classe ...
    DB-->>Repo: Saved Entity
    Repo-->>Service: Saved Entity
    Service-->>Controller: Saved Entity
    Controller-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON)
